          "question_html": "The diluted wine contains only 8 liters of wine and the rest is water. A new mixture whose concentration is 30%, is to be  formed by replacing wine. How many liters of mixture shall be replaced with pure wine if there was initially 32 liters of water in the mixture ?",
          "option_1": "A) 4",
          "option_2": "B) 5",
          "option_3": "C) 8",
          "option_4": "D) None of these",
