          "option_1": "A) 25%",
          "option_2": "B) 30%",
          "option_3": "C) 17%",
          "option_4": "D) 19%",
          "answer": "A) 25%",
          "explanation_html": "<div class='ansDivBox' id='answer11146'><a class='box-head' href='javascript:showans('11146','Alligation or Mixture')'><i class='icon-minus'></i> </a><span class='highlight'>Answer:</span> A) 25%         <br/><br/><span class='highlight'>Explanation:</span><br/> <p>He has gain = 15 - 12 = 3,<br/>Gain% = (3/12) x 100 = (100/4) = 25.<br/>He has 25% gain.</p></div>"
