          "option_4": "D) 17 litres",
          "answer": "",
          "explanation_html": "<div class='ansDivBox' id='answer21694'><a class='box-head' href='javascript:showans('21694','Alligation or Mixture')'><i class='icon-minus'></i> </a><span class='highlight'>Answer:</span> <br/><br/><span class='highlight'>Explanation:</span><br/> <p>Let initial quantity of milk &amp; water in the mixture are 5x &amp; 4x<br/> 2 litres water is added. <br/> Hence,<br/> New quantity of milk &amp; water will be 5x &amp; (4x+2) <br/> ATQ,<br/> 5x/(4x+2) = 10/9<br/> x/(4x+2) = 2/9 9x = 8x + 4<br/> x=4<br/> Hence, <br/> New amount of water in the mixture = 4x+2 = (4*4) + 2 = 18 litres.</p></div>"
